data.description: The Roanoke features decorative columns across the front of the home, creating a welcoming and distinctive covered portico at the front entrance. The central living area includes a large great room under vaulted ceilings with sliders revealing a standard lanai beyond. The kitchen under vaulted ceilings as well, is set back by the great room and separated by a breakfast bar. The kitchen features a spacious nook and a pantry as well. In addition, this home possesses an expansive formal living room that allows you comfortable dinners with your guests. The three-bedroom, two-bath split floor plan features a master suite with his and her closets, and a private bath with a shower/ tub combination.Located just minutes away from shopping, dining, and entertainment, North Side Village is tucked away in a quaint subdivision off Mann Road. The residents will enjoy access to nearby tennis courts, basketball courts, football fields, and pavilion areas for all types of family gatherings.
